prompt:
根据这张图的排版风格与结构，生成可直接编译的 LaTeX（standalone + TikZ/PGFPlots）。仅输出代码，无需解释。若有不确定参数请做合理近似。

提示信息：Types of sparsity. In random sparsity, any bit may be non-zero. Block-random sparsity assumes aligned, contiguous regions of each row are sparse or not sparse. The degree of block-random sparsity may be lower than the fraction of sparsity when 0s are not fully aligned. We also show random column and random block column sparsity. Block column patterns arise in Deja Vu~\cite{liu2023deja}.
